Healing herbs
Sahilla has lost a lot of strength during her journey through the desert, and the wounds she sustained during her battles with wild animals have gone untreated for a long time. She needs immediate treatment, and that with the most effective remedies.
#subobj 1
Find the necromancer's storeroom
The storehouse with herbs, grasses and other medicines is located in the east of the Necromancer's Desert.
#subobj 2
Get the key
The entrance to the warehouse is locked, but one of the guards should have the key.
#subobj 3
Get the herbs
The healing herbs are in one of the containers in the warehouse. You need to take them from there.
